title: JAN 14 2022 - WE JUST SAW THE END OF THE BIDEN ADMINISTRATION
description:
Big losses for the Biden Administration in the past week signifying the end of his “reign”, Ghislaine Maxwell ends fight to keep John Doe names sealed, Washington DC vaccine mandates to take effect Jan 15, and Baltimore prosecutor Marilyn Mosby federally indicted on perjury.


Here’s your Daily dose of Human Events with @JackPosobiec
